Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要好好幫我做兼差工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作就看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳也可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道真相卻沒有阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止那可怕的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止我姊姊\N茱麗葉·奈緒·張的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（茱麗葉的陰謀）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號，依琳娜·伍茲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是4號，夢宮愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺適合的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就給妳們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎\N幫我做兼差工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要妳們實際穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後寫出\N穿著感覺的報告就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這麼高檔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，很適合妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的賞賜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最了不起的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔，彈來彈去耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這可以賣得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最後是…\N我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？穿穿看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件很可愛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要\N我絕對不要穿這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真掃興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人穿成那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，埃爾斯救…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上這個的妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也以同樣方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還她人情過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本寫真集\N少女的惡作劇PART27
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為刊登了真正的\N加爾德羅貝預科生照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管把臉遮住了\N還是在檯面下大賣特賣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜又被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（與室友的危險關係？)
